start() - Method in class nl.uva.se.imppipes.FilterScaler

StartFilter<I> - Class in nl.uva.se.imppipes
A special type of Filter that has all elements in a List processed by a chain of FilterScalers following this StartFilter.

stopExecution() - Method in class nl.uva.se.imppipes.FilterScaler
Stops all Filters used by this FilterScaler by calling FilterScaler.stopExecution(), clears the list of Filters used by this FilterScaler to delete references to them and stops the next FilterScaler if one is present.
stopExecution() - Method in class nl.uva.se.imppipes.StartFilter
